hadiths[170]{hadithnumber,text}:
3657,"Hazrat Khaddaash bin Sulaama Sulaami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main aadmi ko uski maa key barey mein (husne-suluk ki) wasiyat karta hun. main (har) aadmi ko uski maa key barey mein wasiyat karta hun. main (har) aadmi ko uski maa key barey mein wasiyat karta hun (teen baar farmaya). main (har) aadmi ko uskey baap key barey mein wasiyat karta hun. main (har) aadmi ko uskey talluq daar key barey mein wasiyat karta hun jis ka us sey qaribi talluq hai agar-che uski taraf sey takleef ka samna ho."
3658,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : arz kiya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main kis sey neki karun? aap ney farmaya : apni maa sey. poochhney waley ney kaha : uskey baad kis sey? farmaya : apni maa sey. usney kaha : uskey baad kis sey? farmaya : apney baap sey. usney kaha uskey baad kis sey? farmaya : jo ziyada qaribi (talluq rakhta) ho, phir jo (uskey baad) ziyada qaribi ho."
3659,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : beta apney baap ka haq ada nahin kar sakta magar sirf is surat mein (ada kar sakta hai) ke usey ghulam paey to usey kharid kar azad kar dey."
3660,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Qintaar baara hazar oqiye key barabar hai. har auqiya zamin aur aasman key darmiyan ki tamam chizon sey behtar hai. aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jannat mein aadmi ka darja buland kiya jata hai. wo kehta hai : ye kis wajeh sey huwa? usey kaha jata hai : teri aulad key terey liye duaaey maghfirat karney ki wajeh sey."
3661,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Madi Karb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala tumhen tumhari maaon key barey mein (husne-suluk ki) wasiyat karta hai. aap ney ye baat teen baar farmaai , phir farmaya : Allah Taala tumhen tumharey baapon key barey mein wasiyat karta hai. Allah Taala tumhen ziyada qaribi , phir (uskey baad ziyada) qaribi rishte-daaron key barey mein wasiyat farmata hai."
3662,Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! Aulad par waliden ka kya haq hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo teri jannat aur teri jahannam hain.
3663,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : baap jannat ka darmiyani darwaza hai, chahey us darwazey ko zaya kar lo,chahey mehfooz kar lo."
3664,"Hazrat Abu-Usaid Malik bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke qabila banu Salma ka eik aadmi aaya aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya merey waliden sey husne-suluk ki koi surat baqi hai jis key zariey sey un ki wafat key baad mein un sey neki kar sakoon? aap ney farmaya : haan, unkey liye dua karna, unkey liye (Allah sey) bakhshish ki darkhaast karna, un ki wafat key baad unkey wadey purey karna (jo wo zindagi mein purey na kar sakey hon), unkey doston ka ehtiraam karna aur un rishte-daaron sey sila rehmi karna jin sey talluq sirf unkey wastey sey hai."
3665,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : kuchh Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur unhoney kaha : kya tum log apney bachchon ko choomtey ho? Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney kaha : haan. unhoney kaha : lekin , qism hai Allah ki ! hum to (apney bachchon ko) nahin choomtey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye merey ikhtiyar ki baat to nahin jab Allah ney tumharey andar sey reham ka jazba salb kar liya hai."
3666,"Hazrat Yala (bin Murra) Aamiri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Hasan aur Hazrat Husain (Raziallahu anhuma) daudey daudey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aap ney unhen seeney sey laga liya aur farmaya : aulad bukhl aur buzdili ka baais hai."
3667,"Hazrat Suraqa bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya main tumhen sab sey afzal sadqa na bataaun? teri beti jo (bewa ho kar ya Talaq ho janey ki wajeh sey) terey paas wapis aa jaey, aur terey siwa uska koi kamaaney wala na ho (uskey kharchey bardasht karna afzal sadqa hai)."
3668,"Hazrat Ahnaf bin Qais bin Muawiya (Rahimahullah) key chacha Hazrat Saasaa bin Muawiya Taimi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) key paas eik aurat aai. uskey sath uski do betiyan thin. Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney isey teen khajuren den. (us waqt wohi muyassar thin) usney dono betiyon ko eik eik khajoor di . phir bachi hui (teesri khajoor) bhi do tukdey kar key un (bachchiyon) ko dey di. (baad mein) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney ye waqiyaa arz kiya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tajjub kyon karti ho? wo aurat us amal ki wajeh sey jannat mein dakhil ho gaee hai."
3669,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jiski teen betiyan hon, wo un par sabr kerey. jo kuchh muyassar ho is mein sey unhen khilaaey, palaey aur pahnaaey, qiyamat key din wo uskey liye jahannam sey rukawat bin jaeyngi."
3670,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ki do betiyan jawan ho jaeyn aur wo un sey us waqt tak achchha sulook karta rahey jab tak wo uskey sath rahen, ya jab tak wo unkey sath rahey, wo usey jannat mein zarur dakhil kar dengi."
3671,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apni aulad ki izzate-nafs ka khayal rakho, aur unhen achchhey aadaab (aur akhlaq) sikhaao."
3672,"Hazrat Abu-Shuraih Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah par aur aakhirat par eman rakhta hai to usey chahiye ke apney padosi sey achchha sulook karey. jo shakhs Allah par aur aakhirat par eman rakhta hai to usey chahiye ke apney mehman ki izzat kerey. jo shakhs Allah par aur aakhirat par eman rakhta hai to usey chahiye ke achchhi baat kahey ya khamosh rahey."
3673,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey Jibril (Alaihissalam) padosi key sath husne-suluk ki hamesha takeed kartey rahey yahan tak key main guman karney laga ke wo usey virasat mein bhi shareek thehraa dengey."
3674,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey Jibril (Alaihissalam) padosi key sath husne-suluk ki hamesha takeed kartey rahey yahan tak key main guman karney laga ke wo usey virasat mein bhi shareek thehraa dengey."
3675,"Hazrat Abu-Shuraih Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah par aur uskey Rasool par eman rakhta hai, usey chahiye ke apney mehman ki izzat kerey. aur uski (wajib) mehmani eik din raat hai. mehman key liye apney dost (mezbaan) key yahan (itna arsa) tahrey rehna jayez nahin ke wo (mezbaan) tangi mehsus kerey. mehmani (ki masnoon had) teen din tak hai. teen din key baad wo jo kuchh is par kharch karta hai, wo sadqa hai."
3676,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya : aap hamein (sarkaari umoor ki anjam dahi key liye) bhejtey hain. kuchh logon key paas hum theharte hain to wo hamari mehmani nahin kartey. is barey mein aap kya farmatey hain? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hum sey farmaya : jab tum kuchh logon key paas (un ki basti mein) thehro aur wo tumharey liye wo kuchh mohaiyya karen jo mehman key liye hona chahiye to (un sey) qubul kar lo. aur agar wo aisey na karen to un sey mehman ka wo haq wasul karo jo unhen chahiye tha (ke pesh kartey)."
3677,"Hazrat Abu-Kareema Miqdam (bin Maadi-Kirab) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mehman ki eik raat (mehman nawaazi karna) wajib hai. agar mehman subah tak uskey ghar raha (aur usney mehmani na ki) to ye us (sahibe khana) par qarz hai. mehman chahey to uska mutalba (kar key wasul) kar ley, chahey to chhod dey."
3678,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! main (logon ko) do kamzoron yatim aur aurat, ki halaq talfi karna (takeed key sath) haram thehrata hun."
3679,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalmanon mein behtareen ghar wo hai jis ghar mein koi yatim (zere kafalat) ho aur us sey achchha sulook kiya jaey. aur musalmanon mein sab sey bura ghar wo hai jis mein koi yatim (zere kafalat) ho aur us sey bura sulook kiya jaey."
3680,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney teen yatimon ki parwarish ki, wo aisey hai jaisey usney raat bhar qiyam kiya, din bhar roza rakha aur subah Sham Allah ki raah mein talwaar soonti (jihad karta) raha. main aur wo jannat mein is tarah bhai bhai hongey jis tarah ye dono ungliyan behney hain. (ye farmatey huye) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney shahadat ki ungli aur darmiyani ungli ko mila liya."
3681,"Hazrat Abu-Barza Fuzla bin Ubaid Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey koi amal bataiye jis sey mujhey faeyda ho. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalmanon key raastey sey takleef deney wali chiz ko hata diya karo."
3682,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik darkht ki tehni raastey mein thi, us sey logon ko takleef hoti thi, eik aadmi ney isey hata diya to usey jannat mein dakhil kar diya gaya."
3683,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Jundub bin Junaada Ghifaari) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey samney meri ummat apney achchhey aur burey aamaal key sath pesh ki gaee. mainey uskey achchhey aamaal mein raastey sey takleef deh chiz (patthar, kaanta waghera) hataanaa bhi paya. aur uskey burey aamaal mein wo thook paya jo masjid mein (thookaa gaya) ho aur is par mitti na dali gaee ho."
3684,"Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kon sa sadqa afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : pani pilaanaa."
3685,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din log aur ibne Numer ki riwayat mein hai : jannati log, safein banaey huye hongey. eik jahannami eik (jannati) aadmi key paas sey guzreyga aur us sey kaheyga : falan sahab ! kya aap ko yad nahin jis din aap ney pani manga tha to mainey aap ko eik ghoont pani pilaya tha? chunanche wo (uska duniya mein kya huwa ehsan yad kar key) uskey haq mein shafaat kar dega. doosra aadmi guzreyga, wo kaheyga : kya aap ko yad nahin jis din mainey aap ko wuzu key liye pani diya tha? chunanche wo uskey haq mein shafaat kar dega. ibne Numer (apni riwayat mein) bayan kartey hain : wo kaheyga : falan sahab ! kya aap ko yad nahin jis din aap ney mujhey falan falan kaam key liye bheja tha to main aap key liye gaya tha? chunanche wo uskey haq mein shafaat kar dega."
3686,"Hazrat Suraqa bin Jaasham (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya ke eik gum shuda oont merey hoz par aa jata hai jo mainey apney oonton (ko pani pilaney) key liye (banaya, sanwaara aur) leepaa hai. agar main us (gumshuda oont) ko pani pila dun to kya mujhey sawab milega? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan , haraarat mehsus karney waley , jigar rakhney waley har janwer (ko pani pilaney) mein ajr aur sawab hai."
3687,"Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah Bijli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs narmi sey mehroom raha, wo (har qism ki) khair sey mehroom raha."
3688,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala narmi karney wala hai, narmi ko pasand karta hai, aur narmi par wo kuchh ata farmata hai jo sakhti par ata nahin farmata."
3689,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala narmi karney wala hai aur har mamley mein narmi ko pasand farmata hai."
3690,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (ghulam) tumharey bhai hain, jinhen Allah ney tumharey zere-dast (matehet) bana diya hai, lihaza jo khana tum khatey ho is mein sey unhen khilao aur jo (libas) khud pehantey ho is mein sey unhen pehnao. aur in ko wo kaam karney ka hukm na do jo un par ghalib aa jaaey. aur agar (zarurat key tehat) unhen aisa hukm do to (uski anjam dahi mein khud bhi) un ki madad karo."
3691,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : buri maalikaana sifaat ka hamil jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga (Malik honey key pehlu sey bhi achchhi sifaat waala hona chahiye). Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya aap ney hamein ye nahin bataya ke is ummat mein ghulam aur yatim sab qomon sey ziyada hongey? aap ney farmaya : haan (hongey), lihaza un sey isi tarah izzat ka ravaiya rakho jis tarah apni aulad sey izzat ka ravaiya rakhtey ho (unhen khaah-ma-khaah zaleel na karo). aur unhen wohi khilao jo khud khatey ho. unhoney arz kiya : duniya mein kya chiz hamein faeyda dey sakti hai? aap ney farmaya : wo ghoda jisey to Allah ki raah mein jang karney key liye baandh rakhey, tera ghulam jo terey kaam aaye. agar wo namazi ho to wo tera (musalman) bhai hai (lihaza uska khayal rakhna ziyada zaruri hai)."
3692,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum jannat mein dakhil nahin ho saktey yahan tak key eman waley bin jao. aur tum (kamil) momin nahin bin saktey yahan tak key aapas mein mohabbat rakho. kya tum ko eik chiz na bataun jab tum wo amal karogey to eik doosrey sey mohabbat karney lagogey? aapas mein salam ko aam karo."
3693,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamein hamarey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney salam aam karney ka hukm diya."
3694,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Rahmaan ki ibadat karo aur salam aam karo."
3695,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi masjid mein dakhil huwa jabkey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid main eik taraf tashrif farma they. usney namaz padhi, phir aa kar salam kiya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : [ وَعَلَیۡکَ السَّلاَمُ ], ''tujh par bhi salamti ho.''"
3696,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : Jibril (Alaihissalam) aap ko salam keh rahey hain. unhoney kaha : (وَعَلَیَهِ السَّلاَمُ وَرَحۡمَةُ اللہِ), ''un par bhi salamti aur Allah ki rehmat ho.''"
3697,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab ehle-kitab mein sey koi shakhs tumhen salam kahey to (jawab mein) kaho : (وَعَلَیۡکُمۡ) tum par bhi."
3698,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke kuchh Yahudi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur kaha : [اَلسَّامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا أَبَا الْقَاسِم ِ], ''Abul-Qaasim ! aap par saam ho, yani maut ho.'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : [ وَعَلَیْکُمْ ], ''tum par bhi.''"
3699,"Hazrat abu-Abdur-Rehman Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main kal yahudiyon key paas jaaunga. unhen salam karney mein pehal na karna. jab wo tumhen salam kahin to (jawab mein) kehna : (وَعَلَیۡکُمۡ)."
3700,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur hamein salam kaha jabke hum us waqt bachchey they."
3701,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazeed (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hum chand aurton key paas sey guzrey to aap ney hamein salam kaha."
3702,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya hum eik doosrey key liye (ehtiraam key izhar key liye) jhuka karen? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin. hamney kaha : kya hum eik doosrey sey muaaniqa (gale mila) karen? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin. lekin musaafa kar liya karo."
3703,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab do musalman eik doosrey sey miltey hain aur musaafa kartey hain to eik doosrey sey rukhsat honey sey pehley un ki maghfirat ho jati hai."
3704,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key haath ko bosa diya."
3705,Hazrat Safwan bin Assaal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke yahudiyon key chand afrad ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key haath ko aur dono qadmon ko bosa diya.
3706,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey andar aaney ki teen baar ijazat talab ki. unhen ijazat na mili, chunanche wo wapis ho gaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhen kehalwaa bheja : aap wapis kyon chaley gaey? unhoney farmaya : mainey aap sey us andaz sey teen baar ijazat talab ki thi jis tarah Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein hukm diya hai. (is tarah ijazat talab karney key baad) agar hamein ijazat miley to dakhil hon aur agar hamein ijazat na di jaey to palat jaaeyn. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : tum (apney) is (bayan) par gawah pesh karogey warna main tumhen zarur saza dunga. wo apni qom ki majlis mein aaye aur un sey (gawahi deney ki) darkhaast ki, unhoney Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) key haq mein gawahi di to (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney) unhen chhod diya."
3707,"Hazrat Abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye salam (to hamen maloom) hai lekin ijazat talab karney ka kya matlab hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi koi baat kahey, subhan Allah keh dey, Allahu-Akbar keh dey, Alhamdulillah keh dey ya khaans dey. (maqsad ye hai ke) ghar walon ko malum kara dey (ke main andar aana chahta hun)."
3708,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir honey key merey do oqaat they. eik raat mein aur eik din mein. jab main aisey waqt hazir hota ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz padh rahey hotey to aap khaans detey (jis ka matlab ye hota ke mujhey tumharey aaney ka ilm ho gaya hai aur tum andar aa saktey ho)."
3709,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey (hazir honey ki) ijazat talab ki to aap ney farmaya : kon hai? mainey kaha : main. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main, main."
3710,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney kaisey subah ki? aap ney farmaya : khairiyat sey subah hui, aisey aadmi ki jisney na roza rakha, na kisi bimar ki iyaadat ki."
3711,"Hazrat Abu-Usaid (Malik bin Rabeea) Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) key yahan tashrif ley gaey to farmaya : [السَّلاَمُ عَلَیۡکُمۡ]  unhoney (Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur deegar haazireen‬ Raziallahu anhum ney) kaha : [ وَعَلَیْكَ السَّلاَمُ وَرَحْمَةُ اللہِ وَبَرَکَاتُه ] aap ney farmaya : tumhari subh kaisi hui (kya haal hai)?  unhoney kaha : khairiyat sey hui, hum Allah ka shukar kartey hain. aap ki subah kaisi hui? aey Allah key Rasool ! hamarey maa baap aap par qurban hon ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri subah bhi khairiyat sey hui, main Allah ki hamd karta hun."
3712,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tumharey paas kisi qom ka moazzaz shakhs aaye to uski izzat karo."
3713,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas do aadmiyon ko chheenk aai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik ko dua di aur doosrey ko na di. arz kiya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap key paas do aadmiyon ko chheenk aai to aap ney eik ko dua di aur doosrey ko dua nahin di (iski kya wajeh hai)? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usney Allah ki tareef ki thi jabkey usney Allah ki tareef nahin ki."
3714,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwaa‬ (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chheenkney waley ko teen baar (یَرْحَمَكَ اللہ keh kar) dua di jaey. is sey ziyada ho to us shakhs ko zukaam hai."
3715,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi ko chheenk aaye to chahiye ke yun kahey : ( اَلْحَمْدُللہ ),''sab taarifein Allah key liye hain (Allah ka shukr hai).''  jo afrad uskey paas hon wo kahin : (یَرْحَمَكَ اللہ), ''Allah tujh par rehmat nazil farmaaey.'' wo jawab mein unhen kahey : (یَھْدِیکُمُ اللہُ وَیُصْلِحُ بَالَکُمْ), ''Allah tumhen hidayat par qaaim rakhey aur tumharey halaat durust farmaaey.''"
3716,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi aadmi sey miltey aur wo aap sey baat cheet karta to aap apna chehra us sey nahin phertey they yahan tak key wohi (baat cheet sey farigh ho kar) dusri taraf mutawajjeh ho jata. aur jab koi aap sey musaafa karta to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey haath sey apna haath alag na kartey yahan tak key wohi apna haath alag karta. aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kabhi apney sath bethey huye sey ghutney aagey badha kar bethey huye nahin dekha gaya."
3717,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs apni jagah sey uthey , phir wapis aa jaey to wo us (jagah) ka ziyada haq rakhta hai."
3718,"Hazrat Jaudaan (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney apney bhai sey (kisi ghalati par) mazrat ki, aur usney qubul na ki, is par (na-jayez) tax wasul karney waley jitna gunah hai. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney ye riwayat Muhammad bin Ismail key wastey sey bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sabiqa hadees ki misl (tarah) bayan ki hai."
3719,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat sey eik saal pehley (ka waqiyaa hai ke) Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) tijarat key liye Basraa rawana huye. unkey sath Hazrat Nuaimaan aur Hazrat Suwaibit bin Hurmala (Raziallahu anhuma) bhi they. ye dono hazraat ghazwae-badar mein bhi shareek they. Hazrat Nuaimaan zaade-raah (khaney peeney key saman) key zimmedar they. Suwaibit (Raziallahu anhu) bahut mazaahiya tabiat key they. unhoney Nuaimaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : mujhey khana dijiye. unhoney kaha : Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aa jaeyn (un ki ijazat sey dun ga). Suwaibit (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : (tum ney mujhey khana nahin diya, isliye) main aap ko pareshan karunga. (iskey baad safar key doran mein) unka guzar kuchh logon key paas sey huwa. Suwaibit (Raziallahu anhu) ney un logon sey kaha : kya tum log mujh sey mera eik ghulam kharidogey? unhoney kaha : haan. unhoney kaha : wo ghulam zara baatuni hai. wo tum sey kaheyga : main azad hun. agar uski ye baat sun kar tum ney isey chhod dena hai to (abhi sey kharidney sey inkar kar do aur) merey ghulam ka maamla kharab na karo. unhoney kaha : nahin, hum aap sey wo ghulam khareedeingey (aur soda mansookh nahin kerengey). chunanche un logon ney das oontniyon key iwaz un (Suwaibit (Raziallahu anhu)) sey unhen (Nuaimaan (Raziallahu anhu) ko ghulam samajh kar) kharid liya. phir aa kar unkey galey mein pagdi ya rassi dal di (aur unhen qabu kar liya). Nuaimaan (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : ye shakhs (Suwaibit (Raziallahu anhu)) aap logon sey mazaq kar raha hai. main to azad hun, ghulam nahin . unhoney kaha : usney hamein (pehley hi) ye baat bata di thi (ke tum azad honey ka daawey karogey). chunanche wo log unhen pakad kar ley gaey. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaye to logon ney unhen ye waqiyaa bataya. unhoney qafiley walon key peechhey ja kar un ki oontniyaan wapis kin aur Nuaimaan (Raziallahu anhu) ko (un sey) wapis liya. jab ye hazraat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey to aap ko bhi ye pura qissa sunaya, chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum eik saal tak is waaqiye ko yad kar key hanstey rahey."
3720,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey sath be-takkallufi ka izhar farmatey they yahan tak key merey chhotey bhai sey farmatey : aey Abu Umer Nughair ka kya bana? Imam Wakee (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : Nughair eik perinda tha jis sey wo bachcha kheltaa tha."
3721,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney budhapey key (safed) baal ukhaadney sey mana farmaya aur farmaya : wo momin ka Noor hai."
3722,"Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kuchh saye aur kuchh dhoop mein bethney sey mana farmaya."
3723,"Hazrat Tihfaa bin Qais Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey masjid mein pet key bal soty huye paya to mujhey qadam Mubarak sey thokaa diya aur farmaya : uis andaz sey kyon sotey ho? soney ka ye andaz Allah Taala ko napasand hai."
3724,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main pet key bal letaa huwa tha, merey paas sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) guzrey to mujhey qadam Mubarak sey thokaa dey kar farmaya : piyarey Jundub ! ye ehale-jahannam key letney ka andaz hai."
3725,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi key paas sey guzrey jo masjid mein chehrey key bal let kar so raha tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey qadam Mubarak sey thokaa diya aur farmaya : uth kar beth ! ye jahannamiyon key andaz ki neend hai."
3726,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney sitaron ka thoda sa ilm seekha usney jadu ka eik hissa seekh liya. jitna ziyada (ilme-nujoom) seekheyga utna ziyada (jadu seekhney wala shumar) hoga."
3727,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hawa ko bura mat kaho , wo Allah ki rehmat hai jo rehmat ka baais hoti hai aur (kabhi) azab ka baais bhi, isliye Allah sey uski bhalai maango aur uski burai sey Allah ki panah talab karo."
3728,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala key nazdik sab sey ziyada pasandida naam Abdullah aur Abdur-Rehman hain."
3729,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar main zinda raha to Inshallah ye naam rakhney sey mana kar dunga : Rabaha (nafa) Najih (kamiyab), Aflah (kamiyab), Nafey (faeyda deney wala), Yasar (aasani)."
3730,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein apney ghulamon key chaar naam rakhney sey mana farmaya : Aflaah, Nafey, Yasaar, Raabaha."
3731,"Hazrat Masruq (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : meri mulaqat Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey hui to unhoney farmaya : to kon hai? mainey kaha : Masruq bin Ajda'a hun. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye farman suna hai : Ajda'a shetan hai."
3732,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Ummul-mominin Hazrat Zenab binte Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ka naam Barra (nek khatoon) tha. baaz logon ney kaha : wo apni tareef karti hain, chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unka naam Zenab rakh diya."
3733,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki eik beti ka naam, Aasiya tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unka naam Jameela rakh diya."
3734,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa, us waqt mera naam Abdullah bin Salam nahin tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mera naam Abdullah bin Salam rakh diya."
3735,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey naam par naam rakh liya karo aur meri kunniyat par kunniyat na rakho."
3736,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey naam par naam rakh liya karo aur meri kunniyat par kunniyat na rakho."
3737,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Baqee mein they ke eik aadmi ney doosrey ko aawaz di : aey Abul-Qaasim ! Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski taraf mutawajjeh huye to usney kaha : mainey aap ko nahin pukara. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey naam par naam rakh liya karo aur meri kunniyat par kunniyat na rakho."
3738,"Hazrat Hamza bin Suheb (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aap ney apni kunniyat Abu-Yahya kyon rakhi hai, halanke aap ki aulad nahin hai? unhoney farmaya : meri kunniyat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Abu-Yahya rakhi hai."
3739,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya : aap ney merey siwa apni tamam azwaje-mutahrat (paak biwiyon) ki kunniyat rakhi hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum Umme Abdullah ho."
3740,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laya kartey they aur merey eik bhai sey, jo kam sun tha, farmaya kartey they : aey Abu Umer ! ."
3741,"Hazrat Abu Jubaira bin Zuhaak (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : ye aayat hum Ansariyon key barey mein nazil hui : (وَلَا تَنَابَزُوا بِالْأَلْقَابِ), ''eik doosrey key burey naam na rakho.'' Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (hijrat kar key) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur hamarey eik eik aadmi key do-do teen-teen naam hotey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baaz oqaat unhen un namon sey pukartey to arz kiya jata : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo is naam sey naraz hota hai. tab ye aayat nazil hui : (وَلَا تَنَابَزُوا بِالْأَلْقَابِ), ''eik doosrey key burey naam na rakho.''"
3742,"Hazrat Miqdaad bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein hukm diya ke hum tareef karney walon key chehron par khaak dalen."
3743,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : eik doosrey ki tareef sey perhez karo, ye zibeh karney key barabar hai."
3744,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi main eik aadmi ney doosrey aadmi ki tareef ki to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kaee baar farmaya : afsos tujh par ! tu ney to apney sathi ka gala kaat diya. phir farmaya : agar kisi ney apney bhai ki tareef karni ho to yun kahey : mera khayal ye hai aur main Allah key muqabley mein kisi ko paakbaz qarar nahin deta."
3745,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis sey mashwara liya jaey wo amanat sanbhaalney wala hai."
3746,"Hazrat abu-Masood Aqba bin Amr Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis sey mashwara liya jaey, wo amanat sanbhaalney wala hai."
3747,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi apney bhai sey mashwara talab karey to usey chahiye ke usey mashwara dey dey."
3748,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey liye ajam (gahir Arab) ki zamin Fateh hogi, wahan tumhen aisey kamrey milengey jinhen hamaam kaha jaeyga. un mein mard tehband key baghair dakhil na hon aur aurton ko un mein dakhil honey sey mana karo, magar bimar ya nifaas wali dakhil ho sakti hai."
3749,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mardon aur aurton (sab) ko hamamon mein dakhil honey sey mana farmaya, phir mardon ko tehband key sath hamaam mein janey ki ijazat dey di aur aurton ko ijazat nahin di."
3750,"Hazrat Abu-Mulaih (Aamir bin Usama) Hazli (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke teiswin ki rehney wali kuchh khawatin Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huin , unhoney farmaya : shayad tum bhi un aurton mein sey ho jo hamaamon mein jati hain. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jis aurat ney apney khawind key ghar key ilawa (kisi jagah) apney kapdey utarey, usney apney aur Allah key darmiyan (haya ka) parda chaak kar diya."
3751,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab baal Safa pawder istimal kartey to pehley khaas-ang par khud powder lagatey, phir baqi jism par aap ki ehliya laga detin."
3752,Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baal Safa powder lagatey to sattar key aaza (ang) par khud apney haath sey lagatey.
3753,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon ko waaz (taqreer) Ameer karta hai, ya jisey hukm diya gaya ho (aur us mansab (pad) par muqarrar kiya gaya ho), ya riya-kaar."
3754,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein qissa goi thi, na Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key zamaney mein aur na Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key zamaney mein."
3755,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kuch she'r danaai aur hikmat hotey hain."
3756,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : she'ron mein hikmat ki baaten bhi hoti hain."
3757,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi shayer ki kahi hui sab sey sachchi baat Labid ka ye kalam hai : (أَلَا کُلُّ شَیۡ ءٍ مَا خَلَا اللہَ ، بَاطِلُ), ''Allah key siwa har chiz batil hai."" aur Umayya bin Abu Salt qarib tha ke musalman ho jata."
3758,"Hazrat Shareed Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Umayya bin Abu Salt key sau she'r sunaaey. aap har she'r key baad farmatey : (aur she'r) sunao. aur farmaya : qarib tha ke wo musalman ho jata."
3759,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi key pet ka (burey aur gandey) she'ron sey bharey honey sey behtar ye hai ke wo peep sey bhara huwa ho jis sey wo bimar ho jaey. riwayat key Raavi Hafs ney [ یَرِیَه ] key lafz bayan nahin kiye."
3760,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Aadmi key pet ka she'ron sey bharey honey sey behtar ye hai ke wo peep sey bhara huwa ho jis sey wo bimar ho jaey."
3761,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab sey bada jhoot bolney wala wo shakhs hai ke eik aadmi ney doosrey ki tauheen ki to usney (jawab mein) purey qabiley ki tauheen ki (ye sab sey bada jhoota hai). aur wo aadmi jo apney baap sey nasbi talluq todtaa hai aur apni maa ko bad-kar qarar deta hai."
3762,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Abdullah bin Qais Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney narad (chusar) khelaa, usney Allah ki aur uskey Rasool ki nafarmani ki."
3763,"Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney narad (chusar), usney goya apna haath khinzir key gosht aur khoon sey aalooda kiya."
3764,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dekha ke eik aadmi eik perindey ka peechha kar raha hai to farmaya : eik shetan doosrey shetan ka peechha kar raha hai."
3765,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko kabootar ka peechha kartey dekha to farmaya : eik shetan doosrey shetan ka peechha kar raha hai.
3766,"Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko kabootar key peechhey (bhaagtey) dekha to farmaya : shetan, shetan ka peechha kar raha hai."
3767,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko kabootar ka peechha kartey dekha to farmaya : shetan , shetan ka peechha kar raha hai."
3768,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar tumhen malum ho jaey ke tanhai mein kya kya (kharabi aur nuqsan) hai to koi shakhs raat ko akela safar na karey.
3769,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum sotey ho to gharon mein aag (jalti) na chhoda karo."
3770,Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Madina Munawra main eik ghar ko aag lag gaee jabke ghar waley ghar mein they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko unkey haadisey ki khabar hui to aap ney farmaya : ye aag tumhari dushman hai. jab tum soney lago to isey bujha diya karo.
3771,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein (bahut sey kamon ka) hukm diya, aur (bahut sey kamon sey) mana farmaya. aap ney hamein ye hukm bhi diya ke (sotey waqt) chiragh bujha diya karen."
3772,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raastey par qiyam na karo, na wahan qazaey-hajat (peshaab-paakhaana) karo."
3773,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar Taiyaar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab safar sey tashrif latey to hum (bachchey) bhi aap ka istaqbal kartey, chunanche (eik baar) main aur Hasan ya Husain (Raziallahu anhuma) istaqbal karney walon mein shamil they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hum mein sey eik ko (sawari par) apney aagey aur doosrey ko apney peechhey sawar kar liya yahan tak key hum Madina pahunch gaey."
3774,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apni tehriron par mitti dal diya karo, ye kamiyabi ka baais hoga. mitti barkat wali chiz hai."
3775,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum teen afrad ho to do aadmi apney (teesrey) sathi ko chhod kar sargoshi na karen kyonkey is sey usey gham (aur afsos) hoga."
3776,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is baat sey mana farmaya ke do aadmi teesrey ko chhod kar aapas mein sargoshi karen."
3777,Sufiyan bin Ooyena (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : mainey Hazrat Amr bin Dinar sey kaha : aap ney Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) ko farmatey huye suna hai : eik aadmi teer ley kar masjid mein sey guzra to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : in key paikaan (teer ki nok) pakad lo. unhoney jawab diya : haan.
3778,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs teer ley kar hamari masjid mein ya hamarey bazar mein sey guzrey to usey chahiye ke unkey paikaan (teer ki nok) haath sey pakad ley, aisa na ho ke kisi musalman ko kuch nuksan pahunchey."
3779,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Quran Karim (sehat key sath) padhney mein mahir (qiyamat key din) moazzaz neku-kaar farishton key sath hoga. aur jo shakhs isey atak atak kar padhta hai aur isey padhney mein mashaqqat hoti hai, uskey liye dugna ajr hai."
3780,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Quran waley (Haafiz ya Qaari) sey (qiyamat key din) jannat mein dakhil hotey waqt kaha jaeyga : Quran padhta ja aur (jannat key darjaat mein) chadhta ja. wo padhta jaeyga aur har aayat key sath eik eik darja buland hota chala jaeyga yahan tak key usey jo aakhiri aayat yad hai, wo bhi padh ley."
3781,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din Quran Majeed aisey mard ki shakal mein aayega jis ka rang uda huwa ho. aur kaheyga : main wohi hun jisney tujhey raat ko bedaar rakha aur din ko piyasa rakha."
3782,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum mein sey kisi ko ye baat pasand hai ke jab wo ghar jaey to usey ghar mein teen badi badi moti tazi hamila oontniyaan milen? hamney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : agar koi namaz mein teen aayaten padh ley to wo uskey liye teen badi badi moti tazi hamila oontniyon sey behtar hain."
3783,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Quran ki misal ghutna bandhey huye oonton ki si hai. agar Malik unkey bandhanon key zariey sey un ki hifazat kerega to unhen apney qabu mein rakhega , aur agar unkey bandhan khol dega to wo bhag jaeyngey."
3784,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : Allah Taala farmata hai : mainey namaz ko apney aur apney bandey key darmiyan aadha aadha taqseem kar liya hai. wo aadhi merey liye hai aur aadhi merey bandey key liye. aur merey bandey ko wo milega jo wo maangta hai. unhoney kaha : uskey baad Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : padho, banda kehta hai : (الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ),'sab taarifein jahano key Malik aur paalney waley key liye hain.'' to Allah Taala farmata hai : merey bandey ney meri tareef ki aur merey bandey ko wo milega jo wo maangey. banda kehta hai :  (الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ),''bahut meharban, nihayat reham karney wala.''to Allah Taala farmata hai : merey bandey ney meri sanaa ki aur merey bandey ko wo milega jo wo maangey. banda kehta hai : (مَالِكِ يَوْمِ الدِّينِ), ''jaza key din ka Malik hai.'' Allah Taala farmata hai : merey bandey ney meri azmat bayan ki. ye (sab tareef) merey liye hai. aur ye aayat merey darmiyan aur merey bandey key darmiyan nisf nisf (aadhi aadhi) hai. (yani jab) banda kehta hai : (إِيَّاكَ نَعْبُدُ وَإِيَّاكَ نَسْتَعِينُ), ''hum sirf teri hi ibadat kartey hain aur sirf tujh hi sey madad maangtey hain.'' to ye merey aur bandey key darmiyan nisf nisf (aadha aadha) hai. aur merey bandey ko wo milega jo usney manga. aur sura ki (baqi) aakhiri aayaat merey bandey key liye hain. (phir) banda kehta hai : (اهْدِنَا الصِّرَاطَ الْمُسْتَقِيمَ صِرَاطَ الَّذِينَ أَنْعَمْتَ عَلَيْهِمْ غَيْرِ الْمَغْضُوبِ عَلَيْهِمْ وَلَا الضَّالِّينَ),''hamein sidha raasta dikha, un logon ka raasta jin par tu ney inaam kiya, jin par tera ghazab nahin huwa aur na wo gumrah huye.'' (Allah taala farmata hai : ) ye merey bandey ka hissa hai aur merey bandey ko wo milega jo usney manga."
3785,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed bin Muaalli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : kya main masjid sey nikalney sey pehley tujh ko Quran Majeed ki sab sey badi sura na sikha dun? (iskey baad jab) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid sey bahar tashrif ley janey lagey to mainey aap ko yad dahani karaai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ) yehi سبع مثانی (saat, bar-bar dohrani janey wali aayaat) hain aur yehi Quraane-Azeem hai jo mujhey diya gaya hai."
3786,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Quran Majeed main eik sura hai jiski tees aayaten hain. usney apney padhney waley ki shafaat ki yahan tak key uski maghfirat ho gaee (wo sura hai) (تَبَارَكَ الَّذِیْ بِیَدِہِ الْمُلْك)."
3787,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (قُلْ هُوَ اللہُ اَحَدٌ) (Sura Ikhlas) tihai Quran key barabar hai."
3788,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (قُلْ هُوَ اللہُ اَحَدٌ) (Sura Ikhlas) Quran key teesrey hissey key barabar hai."
3789,"Hazrat Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ , الْوَاحِدُ الصَّمَدُ ) tihai Quran key barabar hai."
3790,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya main tumhen aisa amal na bataun jo tumharey aamaal mein sab sey behtar, tumharey badshah (Allah Taala) ko sab sey ziyada pasand, tumharey darjaat ko sab sey ziyada buland karney wala aur tumharey liye sona aur chaandi (Allah ki raah mein) deney sey behtar aur is baat sey bhi behtar hai ke tum apney dushman ka muqabla karo aur un ki gardanen kaato aur wo tumhari gardanen kaatein? Sahaba ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! wo kya hai? aap ney farmaya : Allah ka zikr. Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aadmi koi aisa amal nahin kar sakta jo Allah key azab sey najat deney mein Allah key zikr sey badh kar muassarr ho."
3791,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo log bhi Allah Taala ka zikr karney bethtey hain, unhen farishtey gher letey hain aur un par rehmat chha jati hai, aur un par sakeenat nazil hoti hai, aur Allah Taala unka zikr un (farishton) mein farmata hai jo uskey paas hotey hain."
3792,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala farmata hai : main apney bandey key sath hota hun, jab wo mera zikr karta hai aur uskey hont merey zikr key sath harkat kartey hain."
3793,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik Erabi (dehati) (dehati) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya : Islam mein nek aamaal bahut ziyada hain (main un sab ko jaisa ki haq tha ada nahin kar sakta). mujhey eik baat bata dijiye jisey main mazbooti sey pakad lun. aap ney farmaya : teri zaban hamesha Allah key zikr sey tar rahey."
3794,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney gawahi di ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab banda kehta hai : ( لَا اِلٰه اِلاَّ اللہُ وَاللہُ أَکْبَرُ ), ''Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, aur Allah sab sey bada hai.'' to Allah farmata hai : merey bandey ney sach kaha, merey siwa koi mabood nahin aur main sab sey bada hun. aur jab banda kehta hai : ( لَا اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللہُ وَحْدَہٗ ), ''akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin.'' to wo farmata hai : merey bandey ney sach kaha, mujh akeley key siwa koi mabood nahin. jab banda kehta hai : ( لَا اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللہُ لَا شَرِیْكَ لَه ), ''Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, uska koi shareek nahin.'' to wo farmata hai : merey bandey ney sach kaha, merey siwa koi mabood nahin aur mera koi shareek nahin. jab wo kehta hai :( لَا اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللہُ لَهُ الْمُلْكُ وَلَهُ الْحَمْدُ ), ''Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, badshahi usi key liye hai, aur tareef bhi usi ki hai.'' to wo farmata hai : merey bandey ney sach kaha, merey siwa koi mabood nahin, badshahi merey hi liye hai aur tareef bhi meri hi hai. jab banda kehta hai : ( لَااِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللہُ وَلَاحَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلاَّ بِاللہِ ), ''Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, aur Allah ki tofiq key baghair gunah sey bachao nahin, aur neki ki taqat nahin.'' to Allah Taala farmata hai : merey bandey ney sach kaha , merey siwa koi mabood nahin, aur meri tofiq key baghair (gunah sey) bachao nahin, aur (neki ki) taqat nahin.(Raavi hadees) Abu-Is'haq (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : iskey baad (merey ustaad) Aghrar ney (hadees bayan kartey huye) eik jumla farmaya jisey mein samajh na saka, chunanche mainey Abu-Jafar sey kaha : (ustaad sahab ney) kya farmaya hai? unhoney kaha : ye farmaya hai : jisey maut key waqt ye kalimaat nasib ho gaey usey aag nahin chhueygi."
3795,"Hazrat Yahya bin Talha (Rahimahullah) ney apni walida Hazrat (Umme Suada Al Murriyya ( اُمّ سُعدٰی مُرِّیَّہ)) (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat kiya, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat key baad (eik dafa) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) key paas sey guzrey to farmaya : aap kyon pareshan hain? kya aap ko apney chacha zaad (Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) key Ameerul-momeneen banney sey nagawari mehsus hui hai? Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : nahin, balke (baat ye hai ke) mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna tha ke aap ney farmaya : mujhey eik kalima malum hai jisey agar koi shakhs apni maut key waqt keh ley to wo uskey namaae-aamaal ka Noor bin jata hai, aur maut key waqt uski wajeh sey uskey jism aur jaan ko rahat hasil hoti hai. (afsos is baat ka hai ke) main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat tak aap sey wo kalima daryaft na kar saka. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey wo kalima malum hai. ye wohi hai jisey kehney ka aap ney apney chacha  (Abu-Talib) ko (uski maut key waqt) farmaya tha. agar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ilm hota ke koi aur kalima uskey liye najat ka ziyada sabab bin sakta hai to aap usey wohi (koi aur kalima) padhney ka hukm detey."
3796,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo insan is chiz ki gawahi deta huwa faut ho ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) Allah ka Rasool hun, aur ye gawahi uska dil yaqin sey dey raha ho to Allah Taala zarur uski maghfirat farma dega."
3797,"Hazrat Umme Haani (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (لَا اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللہُ) sey badh kar (afzal) koi amal nahin aur ye kisi gunah ko baqi nahin chhodta."
3798,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney eik din mein sau baar ye alfaz kahey : (لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ لَهُ الْمُلْكُ وَلَهُ الْحَمْدُ وَهُوَ عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ قَدِيرٌ), ''akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, uska koi shareek nahin, badshahi usi ki hai aur tareef bhi usi ki hai, aur wo har chiz par khub qadir hai.'' usey das ghulam azad karney ka sawab hoga, aur uskey liye (namaae-aamaal mein) sau nekiyan likhi jaeyngi, aur uskey sau gunah mita diye jaeyngey, aur in ki wajeh sey sara din, raat tak wo shetan sey mehfooz rahega, aur kisi ka amal uskey amal sey afzal nahin hoga, siwaye us shakhs key jo is sey ziyada zikr karey."
3799,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs subah ki namaz key baad ye dua padhey, usey Hazrat Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki aulad mein sey eik ghulam azad karney key barabar sawab hoga : ( لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ لَهُ الْمُلْكُ وَلَهُ الْحَمْدُ بِيَدِهِ الْخَيْرُ وَهُوَ عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ قَدِيرٌ ), ''Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, wo akela hai, uska koi shareek nahin, badshahi usi ki hai aur tareef bhi usi ki hai, usi key haath mein bhalai hai aur wo har chiz par khub qadir hai.''"
3800,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab sey afzal zikr (لَااِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللہُ) hai, aur sab sey afzal dua ( اَلْحَمْدُ لِلّہِ ) hai."
3801,"Hazrat Qudaama bin Ibrahim Jamhi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke wo Hazrat Abdullah bin umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhuma) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa kartey they jabke wo ladkey they aur unhoney asfar key rangey huye kapdey pehney huye they. (eik baar) Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney unhen hadees sunai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bayan farmaya : Allah key eik bandey ney kaha : ( يَا رَبِّ لَكَ الْحَمْدُ كَمَا يَنْبَغِي لِجَلَالِ وَجْهِكَ وَلِعَظِيمِ سُلْطَانِكَ ), ''aey merey Rab ! main teri tareef karta hun jaisey teri zaat ki azeem shaan aur teri azeem saltanat key laaiq hai.'' ye kalam (aamaal likhney waley) dono farishton key liye mushkil ho gaya. unhen pata na chala ke usey kis tarah likhen (kyonkey Allah Taala ki zaat ki azmat aur uski saltanat aur iqtidar ki shoukat ki pemaaish mumkin nahin ke itni tareef likh detey). wo ooper aasmano mein gaey aur arz kiya ! ya Rab ! terey bandey ney eik baat kahi hai, hamein malum nahin ke usey kis tarah likhen. Allah Taala ney farmaya, halanke usey ziyada malum tha jo uskey bandey ney kaha : merey bandey ney kya kaha? unhoney kaha : ya Rab ! usney kaha : aey merey Rab ! main teri tareef karta hun jaisey teri zaat ki azeem shaan aur teri azeem saltanat key shayaane shayaan hai. Allah ney un (farishton) sey farmaya : isey aisey hi likh do jaisey merey bandey ney kaha hai yahan tak key jab wo mujhey milega to main khud usey iska sawab dunga."
3802,"Hazrat Wayl bin Hujr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz ada ki. (namaz key doran mein) eik aadmi ney kaha : (الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ حَمْدًا كَثِيرًا طَيِّبًا مُبَارَكًا فِيهِ), ''sab tareef Allah key liye hai, bahut ziyada tareef jo paak aur barkaton wali hai.'' jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz sey farigh huye to farmaya : ye alfaz kis ney kahey they? us aadmi ney kaha : mainey (kahey they). aur mera irada to neki ka tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : unkey liye aasman key darwazey khul gaey they aur in (alfaz) key arsh tak pahunchney mein koi chiz rukawat nahin bani."
3803,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab koi achchi chiz (ya achchhi soorate-haal) dekhtey to farmatey : ( الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِي بِنِعْمَتِهِ تَتِمُّ الصَّالِحَاتُ ), ''sab taarifein us Allah key liye jis key Fazal aur inaam sey nek kaam (aur maqasid) purey hotey hain.'' aur jab koi naa-pasandida chiz (ya buri soorate-haal) samney aati to farmatey : ( الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ عَلَى كُلِّ حَالٍ ), ''har haal mein Allah ki tareef aur uska shukar hai.''"
3804,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ( الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ عَلَى كُلِّ حَالٍ رَبِّ أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْ حَالِ أَهْلِ النَّارِ ), ''har haal mein Allah ka shukar hai, aey Allah ! ehale jahannam key haal sey teri panah ka Talib hun.''"
3805,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Allah bandey ko koi nemat deta hai aur banda Alhamdulillah kehta hai to bandey ney jo (shukar) ada kiya, wo milney wali nemat sey afzal hota hai."
3806,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : do kalimaat aisey hain jo zaban par halkey hain, (aamaal key) meezaan (taraazu) mein bhari hain, Rahmaan ko piyarey hain : ( سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ وَبِحَمْدِهِ سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ الْعَظِيمِ ), ''main Allah ki pakizgi bayan karta hun aur uski tareef karta hun, paak hai Allah azmaton wala.''"
3807,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo paudhaa laga rahey they ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unkey paas sey guzrey aur farmaya : Abu-Hurera ! kya laga rahey ho? mainey kaha : paudhaa laga raha hun. aap ney farmaya : kya main tumhen is sey behtar paudhey na bataun? Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : ji haan Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : kaho : (سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ وَلَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَاللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ) in mein sey har har kalimey key iwaz jannat main tumharey liye eik eik darkht laga diya jaaeyga."
3808,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Juweriya binte Haris (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) subah ki namaz padh kar unkey paas sey guzrey to wo Allah ka zikr kar rahi thin. jab din chadhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dobara tashrif laye to wo isi tarah (zikre Ilaahi mein) masroof thin. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey paas sey janey key baad mainey chaar kalimaat teen teen baar kahey hain jo tumharey kiye huye zikr sey (sawab mein) ziyada (ya farmaya : ) wazan mein ziyada hain. [ سُبۡحَانَ اللہِ عَدَدَ خَلۡقِہٖ سُبۡحَانَ اللہِ رِضَا نَفۡسِہٖ , سُبۡحَانَ اللہِ زِنَہَ عَرۡشِہٖ , سُبۡحَانَ اللہِ مِدَادَ کَلِمَاتِہٖ ], ''mqain Allah ki tasbeehaat karta hun uski makhluq ki tadaad key barabar, main Allah ki tasbeehaat karta hun uski zaat ki khushnoodi key mutabiq, main Allah ki paakizgi bayan karta hun uskey arsh key wazan key barabar, main Allah ki taqdees karta hun us (ki tareef) key kalimaat ki siyahi key barabar.''"
3809,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum log Allah ki azmat ka jo zikr kartey ho, yani tasbih (سُبْحَانَ اللہِ), tahleel ( لا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللہ) aur tahmeed (اَلْحَمْدُللہ) key alfaz kehtey ho, wo arsh key ird-gird chakkar lagatey hain. un ki aisi bhinbhinahat hoti hai jaisey shehad ki makkhiyon ki bhinbhinahat. wo apney kehney waley ka (Allah key darbar mein) zikr kartey hain. kya tum nahin chahtey ke (Allah key darbar mein) tumhara zikr hota rahey?"
3810,"Hazrat Umme Haani (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey koi (aasan sa) amal bataiye kyonkey main boodhi aur kamzor ho gaee hun aur mera badan bhari ho gaya hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sau baar (اَللہُ اَکْبَرُ) keh, sau baar (اَلْحَمْدُللہ) keh, sau baar (سُبْحَانَ اللہ) keh. ye lagaam aur kaathi samet sau ghodey Allah ki raah mein deney sey behtar hai, sau oont (Allah ki raah mein qurban kerney) sey behtar hai, aur sau ghulam azad karney sey behtar hai."
3811,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chaar kalimaat sab sey afzal hain. jis kalime sey bhi shuru karo koi harj nahin, ( سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ وَلَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَاللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ )."
3812,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs sau baar ( سُبْحَانَ اللہِ وَبِحَمْدِہ ) kahey , uskey gunah maaf ho jaeyngey agar-che samandar key jhaag ki tarah (be-shumar) hon."
3813,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : (سُبْحَانَ اللہِ وَاَلْحَمْدُللہ وَلَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللہُ وَاللہُ اَکْبَرُ) padhtey raha karo. in kalimaat ki wajeh sey gunah is tarah khatam ho jatey hain jis tarah darkht sey pattey jhad jatey hain."
3814,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik majlis mein sau martaba (ye istighfar kehtey huye) shumar kartey they : (رَبِّ اغْفِرْلِی وَتُبْ عَلَیَّ اِنَّكَ أَنْتَ التَّوَّابُ الرَّحِیْمُ), ''aey merey Rab ! mujhey bakhsh dey aur meri tauba qubul farma, be-shak to bahut tauba qubul karney wala, nihayat meharban hai.''"
3815,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main eik din mein sau martaba Allah Taala sey bakhshish ki darkhaast aur tauba karta hun."
3816,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main eik din mein sattar martaba Allah Taala sey bakhshish ki darkhaast aur tauba karta hun."
3817,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main apney ghar walon sey durust zaban istimal karta tha. (maamuli baat par un par ghussa aa jata aur unhen daant jhidak deta), unkey siwa kisi sey ye ravaiya nahin hota tha. mainey ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to aap ney farmaya : tum istighfar kyon nahin kartey? eik din mein sattar baar istighfar kiya karo."
3818,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Mubarak ho us shakhs ko jisey apney namaae-aamal mein ziyada istighfar mila."
3819,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs istighfar ki pabandi karey to Allah Taala usey har gham sey najat deta hai, uskey liye har tangi sey nikalney ka raasta bana deta hai aur usey aisi jagah sey rozi deta hai jahan sey us ko guman nahin hota."
3820,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : aey Allah ! mujhey un logon mein shamil farma jo jab neki kartey hain to unhen khushi hoti hai aur jab gunah kartey hain to istighfar kartey hain."
3821,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Tabarak w taala farmata hai : jo shakhs neki karta hai usey das gunah (ajr) milega aur main (is sey) ziyada bhi dey deta hun. aur jo shakhs gunah karta hai to gunah ka badla uskey barabar hai (ziyada nahin) ya main (wo gunah bhi) maaf kar deta hun. aur jo shakhs eik baalisht merey qarib aata hai, main us sey eik haath qarib aata hun aur jo shakhs mujh sey eik haath qarib hota hai, main us sey do haath qarib hota hun. aur jo meri taraf chal kar aata hai, main uski taraf bhag kar aata hun. jo shakhs mujh sey zamin bhar gunah ley kar miley lekin merey sath kisi chiz ko shareek na karta ho, main usey itni hi maghfirat ley kar milta hun."
3822,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : AllahTaala farmata hai : main apney bandey key guman key mutabiq (us sey maamla karta) hun, aur jab wo mujhey yad karta hai to main uskey sath hota hun. agar wo mujhey apney dil mein yad karta hai to main bhi usey dil mein yad karta hun. aur agar wo kisi jamaat mein mera zikr karta hai to main un sey behtar (farishton ki) jamaat mein uska zikr karta hun. aur agar wo eik baalisht merey qarib aata hai to main eik haath uskey qarib aata hun, aur agar wo meri taraf chal kar aata hai to main uski taraf daudta huwa aata hun."
3823,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Adam key betey ka har amal (sawab mein) badhta hai. (yani) eik neki das gunaa sey saat sau gunaa tak badhti hai. Allah Taala farmata hai : siwaye rozey key kyonkey wo (khalis) merey liye hota hai aur main hi uska badla dunga."
3824,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey ( لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ ) padhtey suna. aap ney farmaya : aey Abdullah bin Qais (Abu-Musa) ! kya main tujhey jannat key khazanon mein sey eik khazaney ka pata na dun? mainey kaha : ji haan ! Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : kaha kar : ( لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ ), ''Allah ki tofiq key baghair na gunah sey bachao ho sakta hai aur na neki ki taqat hai.''"
3825,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : kya main tujhey jannat key khazanon mein sey eik khazaney ka pata na dun? mainey kaha : kyon nahin aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : (لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ)."
3826,"Hazrat Hazim bin Hurmala (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey guzra to aap ney mujh sey farmaya : aey Hazim ! ( لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ ) ziyada kaha karo kyonkey ye jannat ka eik khazana hai."
